**Drunken** | Attribute
__Basics__
The Drunken player is immune to all attacks at night while there is at least one bartender alive.

__Formalized__
Starting: Protect @Self from `Attacks` through Absence at #tavern during Night (~Attribute)
On @(Role:Bartender) Death: Remove `Absence:Drunken` from @Self [Condition: not (@(Role:Bartender) exists)]
Passive End Night: Kill @Self [Condition: not (@(Role:Bartender) exists)]
